cs.CL, cs.SD, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper deals with language models and their use in generating lyrics and poetry, which falls under the category of natural language processing (NLP). Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also discusses the use of machine learning techniques for training language models, which could fall under cs.SD (Sound) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper proposes a mechanism for combining two separately trained language models, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
